Christmas shopping came early during the festive fashion event Nairobi Fashion Market: Christmas Fair.Attendees over the weekend event were spoilt for choice as over 70 designers, craftpreneurs and retailers showcased affordable collections of fashion, accessories, arts and crafts and home d&eacute;cor collections.The edition was the tenth NFM since its debut in 2010 and included fashion shows from design houses including Zaramu, AfroStreet Kollections, Afrostreet by Melanie, Nato Design House.Part of the proceeds from event went to selected charitable causes in the around the country.